# Pillars flank a central firebox. Mantelpiece caps the top. Opening faces +Z.

# --- PILLARS (solid Stone cubes flanking the firebox) ---
C 0 0 0  Stone
C 2 0 0  Stone

# --- FIREBOX BACK WALL (center cube, X=1, sz=0 strip) ---
S 1 0 0  0 0 0  Stone
S 1 0 0  1 0 0  Stone
S 1 0 0  2 0 0  Stone
S 1 0 0  0 1 0  Stone
S 1 0 0  1 1 0  Stone
S 1 0 0  2 1 0  Stone
S 1 0 0  0 2 0  Stone
S 1 0 0  1 2 0  Stone
S 1 0 0  2 2 0  Stone

# --- HEARTH FLOOR (sy=0, sz=1..2) ---
S 1 0 0  0 0 1  Stone
S 1 0 0  1 0 1  Stone
S 1 0 0  2 0 1  Stone
S 1 0 0  0 0 2  Stone
S 1 0 0  1 0 2  Stone
S 1 0 0  2 0 2  Stone

# --- FIRE (glow, above hearth) ---
S 1 0 0  0 1 1  glow
S 1 0 0  1 1 1  glow
S 1 0 0  2 1 1  glow
S 1 0 0  1 2 1  glow

# --- MANTELPIECE (full-width Stone cap at Y=1) ---
C 0 1 0  Stone
C 1 1 0  Stone
C 2 1 0  Stone
